sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as odh-model-controller<br/>Webhook 9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant MSA as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (FIPS)
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>api.ngc.nvidia.com
    participant NVCR as nvcr.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Route: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission (mutating + validating)<br/>TLS, API server cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed (name ≤53 chars, namespace OK)
        K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch event received
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route, Service,<br/>ServiceMonitor, KEDA TriggerAuth,<br/>ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created
        Note over Route: Per-ISVC Route exposed<br/>{isvc}.{ns}.{cluster-domain}
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,NVCR: Flow 2: NIM Account Provisioning
        User->>K8sAPI: POST Account CR (nim.opendatahub.io/v1)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validating admission<br/>(singleton per namespace)
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed
        K8sAPI-->>User: Account created
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch event received
        Controller->>NGC: Validate API key<br/>HTTPS/443, NGC API Key (Bearer)
        NGC-->>Controller: Key valid + model data
        Controller->>NVCR: Get pull token<br/>HTTPS/443, NGC API Key (Basic)
        NVCR-->>Controller: Docker auth token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Secret (ngc-secret),<br/>ConfigMap, OpenShift Template<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Dashboard,MSA: Flow 3: Gateway Discovery (Dashboard)
        Dashboard->>MSA: GET /api/v1/gateways<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (user)
        MSA->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>(user can create llminferenceservices?)<br/>Auth: User Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>MSA: Access review result
        MSA->>K8sAPI: List Gateways<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>MSA: Filtered gateway list
        MSA-->>Dashboard: JSON response<br/>(RBAC-filtered gateways)
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 4: LLM Auth Policy Management
        Note over Controller: LLMInferenceService created by KServe
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy for HTTPRoute<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter for Gateway<br/>(Authorino TLS bootstrap)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Note over Controller: Kuadrant/Authorino enforce<br/>auth on traffic via mTLS
    end
